\begin_layout Standard
Due to evidence of a certain myopia in consumption (
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "MuellbauerRationalityMyopia1988."
literal "false"

\end_inset

), one is more often concerned with the consumer motivations in the short-term.
 The implication of the long-term equilibrium - however - are different
